      '"Guard us?" Elsa wiped her tears. "But I only destroy things!" Silver Frost shook its great head. "That\'s because you\'re afraid. Ice magic mirrors your feelings. The more you fear it, the more it rages. The more you love, the more gentle and powerful it becomes."',
