      'Maya\'s mouth fell open. Blossom stood tall and explained: "I come from the Digital World — a magical world inside the internet. But something terrible has happened. Someone stole the Master Code! Without it, our world will disappear piece by piece." Blossom held up a tiny paw — already half transparent.',
      '"The Code was split into four pieces hidden in four digital zones," Blossom said. "I need you to come with me and get them back. Will you?" Maya nodded without hesitating. "Of course!"',
